{"tid":1190992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"69前上LIHKG新建議","createTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:18:17.000Z","uid":8241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd78ecb3db5d335292791e2768b545de9454bbf","tid":1190992,"uid":8241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"其實見而家咁多五毛三毛上水<br />\n就知事態嚴重 好明顯班垃圾唔夠貨交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能驚無糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以會留啲好低級既言論<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲打都會睇唔過眼屌佢地<br />\n但咁就正中佢地下懷<br />\n佢地最叻拉低大家level<br />\n佢地無糧出無飯開咩都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以建議大家block晒佢地<br />\n耳根清靜 專心討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎五毛入黎 我驚我有啲人block漏左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d28c2275baf2532d68d4a4238d19d815855cc37","tid":1190992,"uid":484,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eff4fc5da03e21270b68aaf30d40e74dd4c566fe","tid":1190992,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}